M|references|Frameworks beat templates — they teach thinking patterns, not copy-paste shortcuts.
M|references|**Structure:** Identify pain → Amplify consequences → Present solution + soft CTA.
M|references|**Best for:** Problem-aware but not solution-aware prospects. The workhorse framework.
